# Sanctum OS — runtime dependencies of the claude-desktop .deb (fetched at
# first boot from Anthropic's repo). Preinstalling them keeps the first-boot
# install a single small download and immune to archive-index freshness.
# Source of truth: Depends of claude-desktop in
# https://downloads.claude.ai/claude-desktop/apt/stable (binary-arm64 Packages).
# The rest of its Depends (mesa, xcb, glib, portals, uuid) ship with GNOME.
xdg-utils
libgtk-3-0t64
libnotify4
libnss3
libsecret-1-0
libxtst6
# tray icon support (Recommends)
libayatana-appindicator3-1
